data.title: MLB Roundup: De La Cruz leads Reds over Marlins
data.meta_description: Elly De La Cruz again battered the Marlins while at bat and on the bases, going 4 for 5 with two doubles, as the Cincinnati Reds routed Miami 8-2 on Tuesday night.Ã‚
